    "media:imagetext": "Glendale Girl\nFlies South\nof Border\nPriscilla Hughes Mullen, of\nGlendale, is having her first\ntaste of overseas travel, flying\nsouth of the border as a Pan\nAmerican World Airways stew-\nardess.\nThe daughter of Mr. and\nMrs. William F. Mullen, 1829\nIdlewood Road, Glendale, is a\nrecent graduate of the airline's\nInternational Stewardess Col-\nlege in Miami, Florida. Wear-\ning her new gold wings on the\nnorizon blue, high fashion uni-\nform, she is serving aboard\nJet Clipper flights from Miami\nto Latin America and the\nbreeze-swept resort islands of\nthe Caribhean.\nPRISCILLA MULLEN\n• stewardess",
